00:13:35.690 --> 00:13:37.840 align:middle line:90%
So I spoke with just the boys.

00:13:37.840 --> 00:13:42.310 align:middle line:84%
So there is also
protection, separation,

00:13:42.310 --> 00:13:45.760 align:middle line:84%
different frequencies
depending where people fall

00:13:45.760 --> 00:13:48.010 align:middle line:84%
and what people's
intentions are.

00:13:48.010 --> 00:13:52.910 align:middle line:84%
So we are not forced to be
with the people who have maybe

00:13:52.910 --> 00:13:54.800 align:middle line:90%
affected our passing.

00:13:54.800 --> 00:13:56.690 align:middle line:84%
I've also spoken
with families who

00:13:56.690 --> 00:13:59.150 align:middle line:84%
