together in a plane

00:13:59.150 --> 00:14:01.610 align:middle line:90%
and they have been together.

00:14:01.610 --> 00:14:04.460 align:middle line:84%
They held hands
all the way through

00:14:04.460 --> 00:14:08.390 align:middle line:84%
and were met by family members
who reached out and grabbed

00:14:08.390 --> 00:14:09.200 align:middle line:90%
their hands.

00:14:09.200 --> 00:14:12.950 align:middle line:84%
And they walked-- they
didn't even crash.

00:14:12.950 --> 00:14:16.880 align:middle line:84%
They were out of their bodies
before the crash even happened.

00:14:16.880 --> 00:14:22.450 align:middle line:84%
So know that each person
is being taken care of.

00:14:22.450 --> 00:14:25.870 align:middle line:84%
>> The role of religion
