00:14:27.970 --> 00:14:29.380 align:middle line:90%
of shoes you've grown out of.

00:14:29.380 --> 00:14:31.900 align:middle line:10%
So be discerning.

00:14:31.900 --> 00:14:34.810 align:middle line:10%
No baby out with the bathwater.

00:14:34.810 --> 00:14:37.720 align:middle line:10%
