00:14:40.240 --> 00:14:41.390 align:middle line:10%
we're talking about here.

00:14:41.390 --> 00:14:47.090 align:middle line:84%
And then there's the
pedantic, legalistic type

00:14:47.090 --> 00:14:48.710 align:middle line:90%
of religious thought.

00:14:48.710 --> 00:14:53.300 align:middle line:10%
>> In karma what happens is
