experiment conjectures.

00:53:57.440 --> 00:54:01.520 align:middle line:84%
But my science is largely
experimental, also

00:54:01.520 --> 00:54:04.970 align:middle line:84%
with some theory
underlying it, where

00:54:04.970 --> 00:54:08.810 align:middle line:84%
